				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Join us and you will become part of a large and diverse department – with faculty from countries all across the world pursuing research across all the major areas in computer science.</p><p>You will also get to work with the brightest students from our thriving undergraduate and postgraduate programmes.<br /><br />Singapore, a cosmopolitan city that is a melting pot of many cultures, is a great place to live and work – offering high-quality, affordable education and healthcare at all levels, as well as very low tax rates.</p><p>There&#8217;s also extensive support for scientific research – with large-scale national initiatives like the Smart Nation project, as well as a wide array of grants that support computing research and development</p>								</div>
